htmlEscape.haxe_doc:
Escapes HTML special characters of the string `s`.

		The following replacements are made:

		- `&` becomes `&amp`;
		- `<` becomes `&lt`;
		- `>` becomes `&gt`;

		If `quotes` is true, the following characters are also replaced:

		- `"` becomes `&quot`;
		- `'` becomes `&#039`;

